node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Jason Capital on September 02, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, standing, aircraft and outdoors.

node.text:
OK Jason, make it look like you’re doing something really important on your phone cuz this pic is gonna look super dope with the jet and the range in the background and it’ll grab the attention of people who are into this material stuff and it’ll also grab the attention of the people who are trying not to be into the material stuff but they can’t help but be intrigued by it too and then when this pic gets posted, be sure to include a caption about how its not about the material stuff like jets and cars which would be super hypocritical because who posts a pic of them with a jet and car and then has a caption about how jets and cars don’t matter hahahaha ok im done love you bye. 

P.S. Do you like Instagram? My team and I are looking for a few more ppl who want to earn a full-time income from home just typing messages on social media. If you’re interested, message me the word “Test”. Thanks!

node.text:
My yoga teacher @bryankest says, “They named the pose “down dog” because dogs don’t give a shit about their own down dog.” He’s referring to the yogi’s who are more concerned with how their pose looks than how it feels. This is my dog @capitalfrenchies in the pic and I can confirm, he does not give a shit about how his own down dog looks either. #Zero #Fvcks #Given 

P.S. Do you live in an apartment? My team and I are looking for a few more ppl who want to earn a full-time passive income from home using AirBNB without owning property. If you’re interested, message me the word “Deal”. Thanks!
